public class Professional extends Adult implements access, PersonInfoDefaultMethod
This class is a subclass of Adult called 'Professional' and implements access and PersonInfoDefaultMethod This class has a nested class called 'professionalLicense' which is used to store the professional's license information it also has access to all the hikes and may be a guide to others
